  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Fantasy Madness: Bloodbath! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this roguelike action-survival game set in a wildpunk World of Fantasy, your goal is to stand against evil forces who want to destroy the natural order. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/cb17d190862cd389012efccac88ab90f.poster.avif?t=1764148760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/cb17d190862cd389012efccac88ab90f.webm?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/cb17d190862cd389012efccac88ab90f.mp4?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect magical crystals to earn new powers allowing you to summon fierce allies, deadly weapons and digest enchanted mushrooms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/5357cd333b661930ce1d032a9fd7c182.poster.avif?t=1764148760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/5357cd333b661930ce1d032a9fd7c182.webm?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/5357cd333b661930ce1d032a9fd7c182.mp4?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bring retribution using wide arsenal of arcane powers granted by beloved Mother Nature:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Magical staves for more firepower? Checked! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bloodthirsty butterflies offering health transfer? Checked! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast-bringing squirrel squad? Ready to serve!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadly vines and roots to stop charging enemies? Of course! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hellish squealing hog for light-speed mobility? On its way! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sweet little carnivore bunnies to rip off throats? As you wish! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to smash down Orcs from the clan of Aluminum Helmets, Dwarves from the BigMine cartel or the Oilmancy Cult? Then go and bring them Bloodbath!!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/b0532a46a4222615107599d0bd01dad5.poster.avif?t=1764148760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/b0532a46a4222615107599d0bd01dad5.webm?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/b0532a46a4222615107599d0bd01dad5.mp4?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now let’s point out a couple of features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play one of several different game modes with unique objectives including Elimination, Survival, Conquest, Capture The Mushroom and more,  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 different biomes, each with its own family of enemies (including bosses), </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique playable champions, each with its own set of skills, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 unique skills, each with a special max-level power (21 skills per champion),  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up to 8 skills out of available 21 to get the most powerful build, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and equip dozens of powerful Runes and Artifacts to improve your skills and earn new powers, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Humor, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cartoonish bloodshed (optional!), </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wildpunk theme (fantasy with an “unconventional” twist), </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn arts, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast action that requires a little bit of reflexes and dexterity.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Fantasy Madness: Bloodbath! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this roguelike action-survival game set in a wildpunk World of Fantasy, your goal is to stand against evil forces who want to destroy the natural order. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/cb17d190862cd389012efccac88ab90f.poster.avif?t=1764148760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/cb17d190862cd389012efccac88ab90f.webm?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/cb17d190862cd389012efccac88ab90f.mp4?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect magical crystals to earn new powers allowing you to summon fierce allies, deadly weapons and digest enchanted mushrooms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/5357cd333b661930ce1d032a9fd7c182.poster.avif?t=1764148760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/5357cd333b661930ce1d032a9fd7c182.webm?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/5357cd333b661930ce1d032a9fd7c182.mp4?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bring retribution using wide arsenal of arcane powers granted by beloved Mother Nature:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Magical staves for more firepower? Checked! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bloodthirsty butterflies offering health transfer? Checked! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast-bringing squirrel squad? Ready to serve!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadly vines and roots to stop charging enemies? Of course! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hellish squealing hog for light-speed mobility? On its way! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sweet little carnivore bunnies to rip off throats? As you wish! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to smash down Orcs from the clan of Aluminum Helmets, Dwarves from the BigMine cartel or the Oilmancy Cult? Then go and bring them Bloodbath!!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/b0532a46a4222615107599d0bd01dad5.poster.avif?t=1764148760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/b0532a46a4222615107599d0bd01dad5.webm?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185180/extras/b0532a46a4222615107599d0bd01dad5.mp4?t=1764148760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now let’s point out a couple of features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play one of several different game modes with unique objectives including Elimination, Survival, Conquest, Capture The Mushroom and more,  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 different biomes, each with its own family of enemies (including bosses), </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique playable champions, each with its own set of skills, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 unique skills, each with a special max-level power (21 skills per champion),  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up to 8 skills out of available 21 to get the most powerful build, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and equip dozens of powerful Runes and Artifacts to improve your skills and earn new powers, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Humor, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cartoonish bloodshed (optional!), </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wildpunk theme (fantasy with an “unconventional” twist), </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn arts, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast action that requires a little bit of reflexes and dexterity.</p></li></ul>",
